{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Fixpoint.Fixpoint_wto</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"codex","href":"../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Fixpoint","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Fixpoint_wto","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>Forward fixpoint computation of an abstract domain over a WTO (which is not memory-efficient).</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module-type anchored\" id=\"module-type-AbstractDomain\"><a href=\"#module-type-AbstractDomain\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"module-type-AbstractDomain/index.html\">AbstractDomain</a></span><span> = <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Signature for the analysis, which is a standard abstract interpretation <code>Cousot&amp;Cousot,POPL77</code></p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module-type anchored\" id=\"module-type-Graph\"><a href=\"#module-type-Graph\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"module-type-Graph/index.html\">Graph</a></span><span> = <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Signature for the directed graph on which we do the fixpoint computation.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Make\"><a href=\"#module-Make\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Make/index.html\">Make</a></span><span>\u000A  (<a href=\"Make/argument-1-G/index.html\">G</a> : <a href=\"module-type-Graph/index.html\">Graph</a>)\u000A  (<a href=\"Make/argument-2-D/index.html\">D</a> : <a href=\"module-type-AbstractDomain/index.html\">AbstractDomain</a> <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"module-type-AbstractDomain/index.html#type-transition\">transition</a> = <a href=\"Make/argument-1-G/index.html#type-transition\">G.transition</a></span>) : \u000A  <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Given a graph, an abstract domain, a WTO computation on this graph, and an initial mapping from locations to pre-state, compute the final mapping from all reachable locations to their pre-state. Note that it is better if the input node is not part of the WTO.</p></div></div>"}